{"tid":2509172,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇返工兄弟每日臨收工嗰陣都會特別急屎？","createTime":"2021-04-29T08:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T08:58:47.000Z","uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f86e8705491bbb1aecdd9e7ad758d987003461aa","tid":2509172,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:58:47.000Z","msg":"又差唔多到咗收工嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日最期待嘅就係第一個衝閘走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住時間一分一秒咁走去個放工時間，唔知點解身體每次都會開始急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但見到其他同事就算迫近放工鐘數，佢地都係冇乜動靜改變，又唔似會急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲仲好似有咗決心要攬埋工作一齊係公司瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係我返工返到身體壞咗？ 定係佢地已經痴哂線<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sadbutsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好，放工前最後一轉廁所記住靜雞雞拎埋袋先好去屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一夠鐘就走唔使睇人面色<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}